('w_body_A1_06','tooth','/tuːθ/','noun','이, 치아','One of the hard white structures inside the mouth used for biting.','He lost a {tooth} when he was six years old.','그는 여섯 살 때 이가 하나 빠졌어요.','tooth','A1','body',1,'tooth smile dental white clean'),
