('w_body_A1_18','foot','/fʊt/','noun','발','The part at the end of the leg used for standing and walking.','She kicked off her shoes and rested her {foot}.','그녀는 신발을 벗고 발을 쉬게 했어요.','foot','A1','body',1,'foot bare floor relaxing shoe off'),
('w_body_A1_19','toe','/təʊ/','noun','발가락','Each of the five small parts at the end of the foot.','He stubbed his {toe} on the corner of the table.','그는 테이블 모서리에 발가락을 부딪혔어요.','toe','A1','body',1,'toe foot barefoot sand beach'),
