('w_body_A1_32','touch','/tʌtʃ/','verb','만지다','To put your hand or finger on something.','Don''t {touch} the hot stove with your hand.','뜨거운 난로에 손을 대지 마세요.','touch','A1','body',1,'touch hand finger surface warm'),
