('w_body_A2_12','eyelash','/ˈaɪlæʃ/','noun','속눈썹','Each of the short hairs growing on the edges of the eyelids.','She curled her {eyelashes} before going out.','그녀는 외출하기 전에 속눈썹을 말았어요.','eyelashes','A2','body',1,'eyelash mascara makeup eye beauty'),
