('w_family_A1_05','sister','/ˈsɪstər/','noun','여자 형제, 언니, 누나, 여동생','A girl or woman who has the same parents as another person.','Her {sister} moved to a new city last year.','그녀의 언니는 작년에 새로운 도시로 이사했어요.','sister','A1','family',1,'sisters girls siblings happy outdoor'),
('w_family_A1_06','child','/tʃaɪld/','noun','아이, 자녀','A young person, especially one who is not yet an adult.','The {child} ran to her parents after school.','아이는 학교가 끝난 후 부모님께 달려갔어요.','child','A1','family',1,'child playing happy outdoor sunshine'),
('w_family_A1_07','baby','/ˈbeɪbi/','noun','아기, 영아','A very young child who cannot walk or talk yet.','The {baby} smiled when she saw her mother.','아기는 엄마를 보자 방긋 웃었어요.','baby','A1','family',1,'baby smile mother arms tender'),
('w_family_A1_08','son','/sʌn/','noun','아들','A male child in relation to his parents.','Their {son} just started primary school this year.','그들의 아들은 올해 막 초등학교에 입학했어요.','son','A1','family',1,'son father family proud outdoor'),
('w_family_A1_09','daughter','/ˈdɔːtər/','noun','딸','A female child in relation to her parents.','Their {daughter} loves reading books before bed.','그들의 딸은 자기 전에 책 읽는 것을 좋아해요.','daughter','A1','family',1,'daughter mother smiling reading home'),
('w_family_A1_10','husband','/ˈhʌzbənd/','noun','남편','The man to whom a woman is married.','Her {husband} cooks dinner on weekday evenings.','그녀의 남편은 평일 저녁에 저녁을 요리해요.','husband','A1','family',1,'husband wife couple smiling home'),
('w_family_A1_11','wife','/waɪf/','noun','아내','The woman to whom a man is married.','His {wife} surprised him with a birthday cake.','그의 아내가 생일 케이크로 그를 깜짝 놀라게 했어요.','wife','A1','family',1,'wife husband couple celebration cake'),
('w_family_A1_12','parent','/ˈpeərənt/','noun','부모','A person who has a child; a father or mother.','Every {parent} wants the best for their child.','모든 부모는 자녀를 위해 최선을 원해요.','parent','A1','family',1,'parent child hug love tender'),
('w_family_A1_13','grandfather','/ˈɡrændfɑːðər/','noun','할아버지, 외할아버지','The father of one''s father or mother.','My {grandfather} tells amazing stories from his past.','저희 할아버지는 과거 이야기를 정말 재미있게 해주세요.','grandfather','A1','family',1,'grandfather senior man family portrait'),
('w_family_A1_14','grandmother','/ˈɡrænmʌðər/','noun','할머니, 외할머니','The mother of one''s father or mother.','Her {grandmother} makes the best cookies in the world.','그녀의 할머니는 세상에서 제일 맛있는 쿠키를 만드세요.','grandmother','A1','family',1,'grandmother senior woman baking warm kitchen'),
('w_family_A1_15','uncle','/ˈʌŋkl/','noun','삼촌, 외삼촌, 큰아버지, 작은아버지','The brother of one''s father or mother.','My {uncle} always brings presents when he visits.','삼촌은 방문할 때마다 항상 선물을 가져오세요.','uncle','A1','family',1,'uncle nephew family gathering happy'),
('w_family_A1_16','aunt','/ɑːnt/','noun','고모, 이모, 숙모','The sister of one''s father or mother.','Her {aunt} lives in a small town by the sea.','그녀의 고모는 바닷가 작은 마을에 사세요.','aunt','A1','family',1,'aunt niece family visit warm'),
('w_family_A1_17','cousin','/ˈkʌzn/','noun','사촌','A child of one''s uncle or aunt.','My {cousin} and I grew up in the same neighbourhood.','사촌과 저는 같은 동네에서 함께 자랐어요.','cousin','A1','family',1,'cousins children playing together outdoor'),
('w_family_A1_18','friend','/frend/','noun','친구','A person you know and like and who likes you too.','She introduced her best {friend} to the whole family.','그녀는 온 가족에게 가장 친한 친구를 소개했어요.','friend','A1','family',1,'friends smiling together happy bond'),
('w_family_A1_19','love','/lʌv/','noun','사랑','A strong feeling of affection for someone.','The {love} between the twins is very strong.','쌍둥이 사이의 사랑은 정말 강해요.','love','A1','family',1,'love heart family warmth tender'),
('w_family_A1_20','care','/keər/','verb','돌보다, 신경 쓰다','To look after someone and make sure they are safe and well.','She {cares} for her elderly mother every day.','그녀는 매일 연세 드신 어머니를 돌봐요.','care','A1','family',1,'care elderly mother helping hands'),
('w_family_A1_21','born','/bɔːrn/','adjective','태어난','Having come into life for the first time.','He was {born} on a cold winter morning.','그는 추운 겨울 아침에 태어났어요.','born','A1','family',1,'newborn baby hospital mother birth'),
