('w_family_A1_23','meet','/miːt/','verb','만나다','To see and speak to someone for the first time or again.','They always {meet} for coffee on Sunday mornings.','그들은 매주 일요일 아침에 커피를 마시러 만나요.','meet','A1','family',1,'family meeting greeting hug reunion'),
