('w_family_A2_01','relative','/ˈrelətɪv/','noun','친척','A person who is connected to another by birth or marriage.','We invited all our {relatives} to the reunion.','우리는 모든 친척들을 모임에 초대했어요.','relative','A2','family',1,'relatives family gathering reunion celebration'),
('w_family_A2_02','couple','/ˈkʌpl/','noun','커플, 부부','Two people who are in a romantic relationship.','The {couple} celebrated their fifth wedding anniversary.','그 커플은 결혼 5주년을 기념했어요.','couple','A2','family',1,'couple romantic happy anniversary dinner'),
